author: rcmatthews
msg: Improved the debugging facilities by holding the indentation within the debug string.  Also the reflector classes can pass out debug details showing how the peers are set up.

author: rcmatthews
msg: Introduced new component - HelpViewer - that is responsible for showing help text. This need to be registered with the Viewer, and can be done via the SkylarkViewer utility class.  Provided a default implementation that will show text as a view, and the ExternalHelpViewer that fires off an external program passing in the help text as the parameter.
